Package: copulapop
Type: Package
Title: Fit and Generate Virtual Populations Using Vine Copulas
Version: 2.0.1
Date: 2026-01-28
Authors@R: person("Rob", "ter Heine", 
                  email = "r.terheine@radboudumc.nl",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Fit R-Vine copulas to your own datasets and generate realistic 
    virtual patient populations for pharmacometric modeling, PBPK simulations, 
    and clinical trial simulations. Preserves complex correlation structures 
    and tail dependencies between covariates. Includes pre-fitted models for 
    international datasets (Netherlands, China, South Korea, Tanzania, USA, UK) 
    with age, height, weight, and optionally creatinine/eGFR. Provides validation 
    report generation to assess copula fit quality.
